1054:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_uart.c ****     (#) There are two modes of transfer:
1055:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_uart.c ****        (+) Blocking mode: The communication is performed in polling mode.
1056:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_uart.c ****            The HAL status of all data processing is returned by the same function
1057:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_uart.c ****            after finishing transfer.
